    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute beauty of a car, and let me tell you, it is in pristine, showroom-ready shape! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and you'd be hard-pressed to find another one this clean. Come take a look and fall in love with your new ride!",
