    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 Coupe, a collector-grade example of the E46 chassis. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, this unit features a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, complemented by a proactively reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. Finished in Alpine White, the factory paint depth is uniform and the undercarriage is immaculate. This vehicle retains its original mechanical bite and corner-exit composure, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
