    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home your dream car? I'm parting with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it's in incredible shape! It has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection. You really have to see it to believe how pristine it is. I've loved every mile in it, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
