    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2-generation Carrera S represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated flat-six era. Featuring the robust 3.8L 9A1 engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), this powerplant is mated to a crisp six-speed manual transaxle, delivering power through a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono package, providing exceptional lateral grip and throttle response. This example is in showroom condition; the paint retains its factory depth and the interior bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. Mechanically, it is flawless, with a documented service history and an undercarriage that remains pristine. A rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade driver's car.",
